<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-TW" class="scroll-smooth">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>中華數位應用發展協會 - 發起人招募</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/chart.js"></script>
    <!-- Chosen Palette: Warm Neutrals & Trust Blue (Slate-50 background, Blue-900 primary, Teal-600 accents) -->
    <!-- Application Structure Plan: The SPA is designed as a persuasive, linear landing page to guide potential founders through the "Why, What, and How" of the association. It uses a top-down narrative: hooking the user (Hero), explaining the problem visually (Vision/Chart), detailing the solution interactively (Mission grid), outlining the commitment (Founder Tabs), and ending with a clear Call to Action (Contact). This structure minimizes cognitive load and drives conversion for the 30-founder goal. -->
    <!-- Visualization & Content Choices: 1. Digital Gap -> Radar Chart (Chart.js): Visually represents the "Digital Divide" mentioned in the text across Personal, Enterprise, and Social dimensions. 2. Missions -> Interactive JS Grid: Dynamically loaded cards for the 4 core tasks, making them explorable. 3. Rights & Obligations -> JS Tabs: Organizes dense text into digestible, interactive chunks. NO SVG/Mermaid used; Unicode emojis serve as icons. -->
    <!-- CONFIRMATION: NO SVG graphics used. NO Mermaid JS used. -->
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; background-color: #F8FAFC; color: #1E293B; }
        .chart-container { position: relative; width: 100%; max-width: 600px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; height: 40vh; max-height: 400px; }
        @media (min-width: 768px) { .chart-container { height: 350px; } }
        .tab-active { border-bottom-width: 4px; border-color: #0D9488; color: #0F766E; font-weight: 700; }
        .tab-inactive { color: #64748B; border-bottom-width: 4px; border-color: transparent; }
        .tab-inactive:hover { color: #0F766E; border-color: #99F6E4; }
        .card-hover { transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease; }
        .card-hover:hover { transform: translateY(-5px); box-shadow: 0 10px 25px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 8px 10px -6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="antialiased">

    <nav class="fixed w-full bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-md shadow-sm z-50">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="flex justify-between h-16 items-center">
                <div class="flex-shrink-0 font-bold text-xl text-blue-900 tracking-tight">
                    🌐 中華數位應用發展協會
                </div>
                <div class="hidden md:flex space-x-8">
                    <a href="#vision" class="text-slate-600 hover:text-teal-600 font-medium transition-colors">願景與挑戰</a>
                    <a href="#mission" class="text-slate-600 hover:text-teal-600 font-medium transition-colors">核心任務</a>
                    <a href="#founder" class="text-slate-600 hover:text-teal-600 font-medium transition-colors">發起人招募</a>
                    <a href="#join" class="bg-teal-600 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-md font-medium hover:bg-teal-700 transition-colors">立即加入</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <header class="pt-32 pb-20 px-4 text-center bg-gradient-to-b from-slate-100 to-slate-50">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-blue-900 leading-tight mb-6">
                共同見證<span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-teal-600 to-blue-600">數位轉型</span>的新時代
            </h1>
            <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 mb-10 leading-relaxed">
                在生成式 AI 與數位技術飛速發展的今天，「數位能力」已不再是資訊人員的專利，而是每個人、每個家庭、每家企業在未來競爭力中不可或缺的基石。我們誠摯邀請您成為我們的初始發起人！
            </p>
            <div class="flex justify-center gap-4 flex-wrap">
                <a href="#vision" class="px-8 py-3 rounded-full border-2 border-blue-900 text-blue-900 font-bold hover:bg-blue-50 transition-colors">了解願景</a>
                <a href="#join" class="px-8 py-3 rounded-full bg-blue-900 text-white font-bold hover:bg-blue-800 shadow-lg transition-all transform hover:-translate-y-1">成為 30 位發起人之一 🚀</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main>
        <section id="vision" class="py-20 px-4 bg-white">
            <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
                <div class="text-center mb-12">
                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-4">為什麼要成立這個協會？</h2>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-lg">
                        本區塊旨在視覺化目前社會面臨的「數位落差」。透過雷達圖，我們可以清楚看見在個人、企業與社會層面，理想的數位應用能力與現實狀況之間的差距，這正是我們必須採取行動的原因。
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-12">
                    <div class="w-full md:w-1/2">
                        <div class="chart-container">
                            <canvas id="gapChart"></canvas>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 space-y-6">
                        <div class="bg-slate-50 p-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 card-hover">
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-900 mb-2">👤 個人端：AI 焦慮</h3>
                            <p class="text-slate-600">面對 AI 浪潮感到焦慮，不知如何運用新興工具提升工作效率，面臨職場競爭力下降的風險。</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="bg-slate-50 p-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 card-hover">
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-900 mb-2">🏢 企業端：轉型困境</h3>
                            <p class="text-slate-600">中小企業渴望轉型以提高產能與利潤，卻普遍缺乏實務的數位應用路徑與專業數位人才。</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="bg-slate-50 p-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 card-hover">
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-900 mb-2">🌍 社會端：資源不均</h3>
                            <p class="text-slate-600">數位資源分佈不均，偏鄉地區或弱勢群體在高速發展的數位時代中，更容易被邊緣化。</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="mission" class="py-20 px-4 bg-slate-50">
            <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
                <div class="text-center mb-12">
                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-4">我們的核心任務 (Mission)</h2>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-lg">
                        本區塊展示協會成立後將推動的四大核心支柱。點擊或瀏覽下方卡片，了解我們將如何成為「數位應用」與「大眾生活」之間的橋樑，並具體落實我們的願景。
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div id="mission-grid" class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="founder" class="py-20 px-4 bg-white">
            <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
                <div class="text-center mb-12">
                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-4">為什麼邀請您成為「發起人」？</h2>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-lg">
                        依法成立全國性協會需集結 30 位發起人。本區塊說明身為創始發起人的榮耀與指標性意義，並透過互動頁籤詳細列出發起人的具體權利與義務，讓您清楚了解參與的價值與責任。
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-16">
                    <div class="text-center p-6">
                        <div class="text-5xl mb-4">🏆</div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2">創始地位</h3>
                        <p class="text-slate-600">您的名字將永久記錄在協會創立史中，並在成立大會獲頒紀念證書。</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="text-center p-6">
                        <div class="text-5xl mb-4">⚖️</div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2">影響決策</h3>
                        <p class="text-slate-600">優先參與第一屆理監事選舉，直接參與制定協會未來的發展方向。</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="text-center p-6">
                        <div class="text-5xl mb-4">🤝</div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2">專業人脈</h3>
                        <p class="text-slate-600">與 30 位來自各行各業、對數位應用有熱忱的跨領域菁英建立深度連結。</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl p-2 sm:p-8 border border-slate-200">
                    <div class="flex border-b border-slate-300 mb-6" id="tabs-container">
                        <button class="flex-1 py-4 text-lg tab-active transition-all" onclick="switchTab('rights')">發起人權利</button>
                        <button class="flex-1 py-4 text-lg tab-inactive transition-all" onclick="switchTab('obligations')">發起人義務</button>
                    </div>
                    <div id="tab-content-rights" class="p-4 block animate-fade-in">
                        <ul class="space-y-4 text-slate-700 text-lg">
                            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="mr-3 text-teal-600 font-bold">✓</span> 享有未來協會正式會員的所有福利。</li>
                            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="mr-3 text-teal-600 font-bold">✓</span> 擁有第一屆理監事之選舉權。</li>
                            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="mr-3 text-teal-600 font-bold">✓</span> 擁有第一屆理監事之被選舉權。</li>
                            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="mr-3 text-teal-600 font-bold">✓</span> 擁有針對協會重要人事與議案之罷免權與表決權。</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div id="tab-content-obligations" class="p-4 hidden animate-fade-in">
                        <ul class="space-y-4 text-slate-700 text-lg">
                            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="mr-3 text-orange-500 font-bold">!</span> 提供身分證影本（依法申請核准使用，僅限籌備用途）。</li>
                            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="mr-3 text-orange-500 font-bold">!</span> 出席（或委託出席）發起人會議及成立大會（預計 1-2 次會議）。</li>
                            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="mr-3 text-orange-500 font-bold">!</span> 繳納入會費與常年會費（實際金額將由發起人會議討論通過）。</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="join" class="py-20 px-4 bg-blue-900 text-white">
            <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
                <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">「一個人走得快，一群人走得遠。」</h2>
                <p class="text-xl text-blue-200 mb-12">
                    如果您認同我們的理念，願意為台灣的數位發展貢獻一份心力，讓我們攜手合作，讓數位應用成為每個人的超能力！
                </p>

                <div class="bg-white text-slate-800 rounded-2xl p-8 max-w-lg mx-auto shadow-2xl text-left">
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-900 mb-6 border-b pb-4">聯絡籌備處</h3>
                    <div class="space-y-4 text-lg">
                        <div class="flex items-center">
                            <span class="w-10 text-center text-2xl">👤</span>
                            <div>
                                <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">籌備發起人</p>
                                <p class="font-bold">張棋鈞</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex items-center">
                            <span class="w-10 text-center text-2xl">📞</span>
                            <div>
                                <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">聯絡電話</p>
                                <a href="tel:0903887999" class="font-bold text-teal-600 hover:underline">0903-887-999</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex items-center">
                            <span class="w-10 text-center text-2xl">💬</span>
                            <div>
                                <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Line ID</p>
                                <p class="font-bold text-teal-600">0903-887-999</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex items-center">
                            <span class="w-10 text-center text-2xl">✉️</span>
                            <div>
                                <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Email</p>
                                <a href="mailto:jimmychang0114@gmail.com" class="font-bold text-teal-600 hover:underline break-all">jimmychang0114@gmail.com</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer class="bg-slate-900 text-slate-400 py-8 text-center px-4">
        <p>© 2026 社團法人中華數位應用發展協會 籌備小組 敬邀. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>

    <script>
        const missionData = [
            { id: 1, icon: "🎓", title: "推廣數位教育", desc: "舉辦 AI 工具、數位生產力軟體之實務講座與工作坊，提升全民數位素養。" },
            { id: 2, icon: "🤝", title: "促進產業對接", desc: "媒合數位人才與企業需求，協助中小企業導入合適的數位解決方案。" },
            { id: 3, icon: "❤️", title: "社會公益實踐", desc: "協助偏鄉或銀髮族掌握基礎數位應用，運用科技縮短城鄉與世代數位鴻溝。" },
            { id: 4, icon: "🏛️", title: "政策建議與交流", desc: "作為政府與民間在數位發展議題上的溝通平台，推動友善數位法規環境。" }
        ];

        function renderMissions() {
            const container = document.getElementById('mission-grid');
            container.innerHTML = '';
            missionData.forEach(mission => {
                const card = document.createElement('div');
                card.className = 'bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 card-hover flex flex-col items-center text-center';
                card.innerHTML = `
                    <div class="text-5xl mb-4 bg-teal-50 w-20 h-20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">${mission.icon}</div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-900 mb-3">${mission.title}</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">${mission.desc}</p>
                `;
                container.appendChild(card);
            });
        }

        const appState = { currentTab: 'rights' };

        function switchTab(tabId) {
            appState.currentTab = tabId;
            const rightsBtn = document.querySelector('#tabs-container button:nth-child(1)');
            const obsBtn = document.querySelector('#tabs-container button:nth-child(2)');
            const rightsContent = document.getElementById('tab-content-rights');
            const obsContent = document.getElementById('tab-content-obligations');

            if (tabId === 'rights') {
                rightsBtn.className = 'flex-1 py-4 text-lg tab-active transition-all';
                obsBtn.className = 'flex-1 py-4 text-lg tab-inactive transition-all';
                rightsContent.classList.remove('hidden');
                obsContent.classList.add('hidden');
            } else {
                obsBtn.className = 'flex-1 py-4 text-lg tab-active transition-all';
                rightsBtn.className = 'flex-1 py-4 text-lg tab-inactive transition-all';
                obsContent.classList.remove('hidden');
                rightsContent.classList.add('hidden');
            }
        }

        function initChart() {
            const ctx = document.getElementById('gapChart').getContext('2d');
            new Chart(ctx, {
                type: 'radar',
                data: {
                    labels: ['個人數位技能', '企業AI導入', '偏鄉資源普及', '長者數位適應', '產業人才媒合'],
                    datasets: [
                        {
                            label: '當前社會現狀',
                            data: [40, 30, 20, 15, 35],
                            backgroundColor: 'rgba(203, 213, 225, 0.4)',
                            borderColor: 'rgba(148, 163, 184, 1)',
                            pointBackgroundColor: 'rgba(148, 163, 184, 1)',
                            borderWidth: 2
                        },
                        {
                            label: '協會期望達成目標',
                            data: [90, 85, 80, 75, 95],
                            backgroundColor: 'rgba(13, 148, 136, 0.2)',
                            borderColor: 'rgba(13, 148, 136, 1)',
                            pointBackgroundColor: 'rgba(13, 148, 136, 1)',
                            borderWidth: 2
                        }
                    ]
                },
                options: {
                    responsive: true,
                    maintainAspectRatio: false,
                    scales: {
                        r: {
                            angleLines: { color: 'rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05)' },
                            grid: { color: 'rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05)' },
                            pointLabels: {
                                font: { size: 12, family: "'Segoe UI', sans-serif" },
                                color: '#475569'
                            },
                            ticks: { display: false, min: 0, max: 100 }
                        }
                    },
                    plugins: {
                        legend: { position: 'bottom', labels: { font: { family: "'Segoe UI', sans-serif" } } },
                        tooltip: {
                            backgroundColor: 'rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.9)',
                            titleFont: { size: 14 },
                            bodyFont: { size: 13 },
                            padding: 10,
                            cornerRadius: 8
                        }
                    }
                }
            });
        }

        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
            renderMissions();
            initChart();
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
